      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAID MY DUES (1) ran below his best last time finishing fourth (30.14) over 520m at this track in a OPEN. Form here at the trip excellent including three wins. Has won three of five starts from this draw. Can bounce back. ROSIE BROWNE (2) was in traffic and missed the frame in a Grade 5 at this track over 601m latest, finishing a 6 length fourth (35.25). Has Box 2 this time where she has a win. Expected to feature on best. REINVIGORATED (7) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 1.75 lengths (41.87) behind Mepunga Lara at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Overdue and is among the main hopes. JUST A PRINCESS (3) is another with top-three prospects.",
